gocraft/dbr provides additions to Go's database/sql for super fast performance and convenience.

```
$ go get -u github.com/gocraft/dbr
```

```go
import "github.com/gocraft/dbr"
```

## Driver support

* MySQL
* PostgreSQL
* SQLite3

